@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eqyjae(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.31) - (v2 + 0.42 - v0 + 0.35)) / wp.abs((tmp + 0.02 / v0 + 0.29)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.21)) / v2)
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.83)) + ((tmp + 0.47 * v2 + 0.18) / (tmp + 0.50 - tmp + 0.06)))
    data[tid] = v0
